Code 1
------

This example shows using of external file also.
Test if variable is negative looks like <<c.isneg>>: `if ($x <
0)`.
So, we can write absolute function <<c.fun1>>:

    <<=c.hh.0, file:GUI>>
    int fun1(int a) {
        <<=c.isneg, x:a>> {
            a += 100;
            return -a;
        }
        else
            return a;
    }
